<h2><a name="bin">bin directory</a></h2>
<p>Used for: holding the program (python scripts)</p>
<p>Location: root/bin</p>
<p>Contains the following files:
<ul><li>tkad_main.py - a wrapper which calls initall.py in case that all the proper libraries are installed. It also provides a basic command line information about the possible options.</li>
    <li>initall.py - the main script - creates the app windows, populate it with appropriate widgets, initialise settings from the hdd, etc</li></ul></p>

<p>Contains the following directories:
<ul><li><a href = "gui">GUI</a></li></ul></p>

